==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Filefish
<hw>File"fish`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any plectognath fish of the genera <gen>Monacanthus</gen>,
<gen>Alutera</gen>, <gen>balistes</gen>, and allied genera; -- so called
on account of the roughly granulated skin, which is sometimes used in
place of sandpaper.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Filemot</ent>⟦br⟧
